OL,4,G0100FKate Winslet: A Quest For
OL,5,     FAuthenticity
OL,6,     GThe reasoning behind Kate
OL,7,     GWinslet's choice of roles.
OL,8,     GThroughout her career, she has
OL,9,     Gchosen to play roles of authentic
OL,10,     Gwomen with complex psyches and
OL,11,     Grealistic bodies.
OL,12,G0215FBlue Road: The Edna O'Brien Story
OL,13,     GEdna O'Brien, 93, reflects on her
OL,14,     Glife, novels and love through
OL,15,     Gjournals read by Jessie Buckley,
OL,16,     Gwith insight from writers like
OL,17,     GGabriel Byrne.
